Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.21,0:00:17.11,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}微风轻吻着脸庞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.48,0:00:20.68,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}用着一种怀念的温柔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.85,0:00:28.85,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}吹干流下的泪珠轻拂而去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.42,0:00:39.63,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}不管是谁 对未来都有着一股不安的期望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.73,0:00:43.64,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}就朝着明天大步迈进吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.98,0:00:51.14,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}GUNPARADE MARCH
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.25,0:00:57.65,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}总有一天会觉醒的 真实之心扉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.75,0:01:03.96,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}现在就伸出双手去感受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.96,0:01:13.96,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}在这开始变化的世界 立刻前往探寻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.04,0:01:20.20,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}牵系着你的手绝不再分离
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.74,0:01:23.01,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}因为有你在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.01,0:01:28.31,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}所以一定找寻的到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.72,0:01:33.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剪刀、石头、布
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.46,0:01:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.23,0:01:41.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.33,0:02:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.52,0:02:42.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「第二话  自我风格」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.86,0:02:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fnsimhei}(各位早安 又是熊本时间了 首先报导幻兽情报)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.10,0:02:49.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fnsimhei}(熊本管区的梅仓小姐)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.03,0:02:50.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.57,0:02:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fnsimhei}(这里是熊本管区 八代地区灾害惨重)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.40,0:02:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速水同学\N{\fs20\fnsimhei}(巨型且强大的6号幻兽)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.77,0:02:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一样的东西就可以吧\N{\fs20\fnsimhei}(昨日已消灭 车辆进出限制解除)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.91,0:03:03.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想说你应该快来了 所以早就准备好咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.78,0:03:05.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思\N{\fs20\fnsimhei}(损失报告日后司令部会择日公开)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.18,0:03:08.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天真的是辛苦你了\N{\fs20\fnsimhei}(以上是熊本管区的报导)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.55,0:03:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏你们打倒怪兽 今年的中元也能好好办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.42,0:03:19.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是很感谢你们呢\N{\fs20\fnsimhei}(谢谢 也祝各位有美好一天)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.53,0:03:21.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.10,0:03:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我差不多该上学了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.30,0:03:27.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天也会等你来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.14,0:03:28.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.01,0:03:36.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本节目是由为人类开拓未来的芝村关系企业所提供
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.41,0:03:39.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速水又输了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.88,0:03:42.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正平常都是这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.12,0:03:44.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是没错啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.12,0:03:49.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗时的速水同学感觉如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.39,0:03:52.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时我都已经自顾不暇了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.93,0:03:54.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以没注意到其他人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.10,0:03:58.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原学姊 你对那样的人有兴趣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.64,0:04:01.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.47,0:04:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉很能引起母性本能呢～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.04,0:04:08.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-所以注意上他了？\N- 一点点啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.88,0:04:13.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么行 原学姊你已经有我了耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.42,0:04:18.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位同学 这似乎不适合当成早上的话题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.59,0:04:20.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壬生屋你脸红了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.16,0:04:25.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未央 什么是母性本能啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.66,0:04:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-好像这样咯\N-好乖好乖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.10,0:04:30.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不纯洁！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.43,0:04:32.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未央 怎么不理我啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.93,0:04:36.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壬生屋比较硬 学姊比较软
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.11,0:04:38.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样会痒啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.44,0:04:40.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个难道是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.44,0:04:42.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是同性之恋吧～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.94,0:04:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该说是女同性恋吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.18,0:04:47.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么？好吃吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.62,0:04:49.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别装傻啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.39,0:04:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是香蕉口味呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.69,0:04:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-喂喂 刚刚吞下去了？\N-还蛮好喝的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.39,0:04:59.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是田边呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.63,0:05:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就是62胜6败 胜率超过九成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.40,0:05:09.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为什么赢不了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.71,0:05:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你的赌运太差啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.98,0:05:15.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的吗…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.15,0:05:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此之外还会是怎样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.72,0:05:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.92,0:05:25.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-喂 还我啦\N-有什么关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.42,0:05:29.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-上面写了什么啊\N-自己看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.49,0:05:30.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.23,0:05:34.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是女孩子的名字呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.93,0:05:37.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这些未成年的不要管啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.93,0:05:41.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得你在转移话题 不过这是什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.00,0:05:43.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会是什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.74,0:05:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们吵死啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.18,0:05:51.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fnsimhei}现在报导八代地区临时对应中心提供的被害情形
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.25,0:05:59.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fnsimhei}7月8日为止 幻兽6号造成305人死亡 523人轻重伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.75,0:06:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fnsimhei}失踪者有800人以上 目前仍在持续调查中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.26,0:06:11.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fnsimhei}关于死者身份的指认 请询问各地紧急事故应对单位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.21,0:06:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,袖子好像有点长呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.98,0:06:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正还会长大 没关系的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.28,0:06:31.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 临时转学过来真辛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.79,0:06:35.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军中好像没在说转学的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.56,0:06:40.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉 我负责普通科 所以不太清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.57,0:06:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家回位子上吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.00,0:06:51.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 现在介绍新朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.07,0:06:55.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天成为各位同学的芝村舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.52,0:07:06.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芝村 是不是那个芝村集团…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.26,0:07:08.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不就是有钱人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.82,0:07:11.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不一定喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.03,0:07:12.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定只是姓氏一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.03,0:07:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.26,0:07:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位同学请安静
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.77,0:07:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那芝村同学就坐那边吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.35,0:07:34.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.62,0:07:45.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就开始上课了 请大家打开课本吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.14,0:08:02.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fnsimhei}(芝村舞 外型漂亮)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.72,0:08:11.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是不要好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.72,0:08:13.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.16,0:08:19.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…芝村同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.89,0:08:23.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的话 由我来带你熟悉这个环境吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.67,0:08:25.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要顺便吃个饭？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.90,0:08:30.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fnsimhei}(法式料理？意式料理？还是中华或日本料理？)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.91,0:08:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的开场白真是老套呢\N{\fs20\fnsimhei}(我们好好聊一聊吧)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.61,0:08:40.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会太积极了啊\N{\fs20\fnsimhei}(刚转学过来 很多事都不熟悉吧)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.45,0:08:41.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-他在说什么啊\N-没错没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.62,0:08:48.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fnsimhei}(我们这样的学生烦恼也多 我很想成为你的助力)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.86,0:08:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 他也这样跟我说过\N{\fs20\fnsimhei}(在这黑暗的时代里)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.73,0:08:52.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是\N{\fs20\fnsimhei}(人跟人之间都要相互扶持)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.23,0:08:56.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田边也被他这样说过啊 真是意外呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.63,0:09:00.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fnsimhei}(你别无误会 这话我可都没跟任何人说过喔)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.47,0:09:01.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多了\N{\fs20\fnsimhei}(你也可以感觉到 这都是命运)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.14,0:09:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像是分离而孤单的灵魂会彼此吸引
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.74,0:09:09.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实你也跟我一样寂寞…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.88,0:09:13.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提醒芝村同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.02,0:09:18.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个男人是看到女生就会开始饥渴的色狼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.99,0:09:23.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学术名是哺乳类泡妞目好色科的濑户口色狼隆之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.26,0:09:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他很危险 遭受毒爪的女孩多不可数
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.16,0:09:29.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守备范围从小孩到老婆婆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.66,0:09:33.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要不是男生都没问题 即使是宇宙人也一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.91,0:09:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你们啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.27,0:09:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像被发现了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.01,0:09:43.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.68,0:09:55.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们班上的女生说话比较毒 这些都是开玩笑而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.69,0:09:59.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芝村同学 你愿意相信我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.07,0:10:06.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芝村同学？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.57,0:10:15.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的训练是基于有新驾驶员的加入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.81,0:10:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以由两人一组 进行双人座HWT操作适应训练
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.22,0:10:29.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本训练的重点在于双方的默契跟合作程度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.06,0:10:32.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-请务必记得这一点\N-遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.83,0:10:35.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么首先由芝村同学跟…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.23,0:10:39.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濑户口有事吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.33,0:10:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我目前的身心状况都是巅峰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.47,0:10:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fnsimhei}(我现在的使命感 可是比那阿苏山的溶浆还炎热)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.24,0:10:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真受不了呢 这才像是濑户口啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.84,0:10:53.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能藉这个机会 展现我的实力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.58,0:10:56.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就先由芝村跟濑户口开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.14,0:11:15.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.41,0:11:27.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.78,0:11:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,启动主系统
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.42,0:11:33.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索敌雷达跟炮火管制系统正常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.99,0:11:36.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假想敌设定记录开启
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.79,0:11:39.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有系统没有异常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.39,0:11:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,训练开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.77,0:11:53.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芝村座机成功打倒幻兽哥鲁戈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.91,0:11:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不错呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.68,0:12:01.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fnsimhei}(我是濑户口)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.68,0:12:04.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fnsimhei}(要一起去看电影吗？)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.42,0:12:08.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fnsimhei}(还是去游泳池玩？)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.52,0:12:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fnsimhei}(还是图书馆比较好？)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.32,0:12:15.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fnsimhei}(小舞有听到吗？)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.43,0:12:19.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冒失家伙！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.34,0:12:30.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芝村 你打错对象咯\N{\fs20\fnsimhei}(连生气的样子也好可爱喔)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.21,0:12:34.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fnsimhei}(你的爱情表现还真激烈啊)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.46,0:12:48.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-她比壬生屋还厉害呢\N-濑户口真可怜啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.07,0:12:55.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速水 刚刚的声音是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.98,0:13:02.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.98,0:13:05.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这样就要对她道谢呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.48,0:13:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是既然她帮了我们 还是道谢一下比较好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.35,0:13:14.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不太喜欢那个人 总觉得她好像很难以接近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.12,0:13:15.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.09,0:13:20.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真稀奇的组合呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.49,0:13:22.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-两个人要准备约会？\N-不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.26,0:13:24.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.90,0:13:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速水同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.13,0:13:31.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果被壬生屋甩掉的话 随时都可以来找姊姊我喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.77,0:13:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会随时安慰你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.28,0:13:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先走咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.52,0:13:43.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芝村同学她没事吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.52,0:13:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她看起来很内向不是吗 而且几乎都没有说话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.29,0:13:51.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我担心她能不能跟大家好好相处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.53,0:13:53.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该没问题吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.53,0:13:56.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的个性其实很活泼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.53,0:14:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说濑户口的事情了 这对他也算是个教训吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.94,0:14:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话 还是呆呆的人比较好\N啊 我指的就是速水同学啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.31,0:14:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他看起来总是漫不经心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.95,0:14:17.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不要随便跟别人说喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.95,0:14:21.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是全部了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.42,0:14:22.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.46,0:14:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你睡觉不用棉被吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.09,0:14:28.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该有一起送来 不过好像还没送到的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.66,0:14:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我把睡衣跟睡袋借你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.70,0:14:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.97,0:14:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就重新自我介绍 我的名字是加藤祭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.47,0:14:39.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,负责5121部队的经理装备跟文书工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.71,0:14:42.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么其他的事情也可以找我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.18,0:14:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.58,0:14:50.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚的说明费 特价算你五百块就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.35,0:14:51.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在身上没这么多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.09,0:14:55.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑、开玩笑的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.19,0:14:57.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用付也没关系吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.63,0:15:01.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得对话有些不搭呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.36,0:15:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芝村舞 我总有一天要追到你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.10,0:15:08.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,声音太大咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.97,0:15:11.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,训练输给她有这么挫折吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.61,0:15:13.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该不可能吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.87,0:15:15.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对要让她迷上我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.38,0:15:19.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种女孩哪里好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.01,0:15:23.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才一定要征服她啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.48,0:15:24.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,征服？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.99,0:15:28.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在的内心正不断燃烧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.02,0:15:29.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.12,0:15:32.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-泷川\N-干嘛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.39,0:15:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在知道你之前所说内心燃烧的意思了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.73,0:15:39.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-所以就跟我一起燃烧吧\N-濑户口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.67,0:15:41.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.40,0:15:45.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着吧 芝村舞！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.68,0:15:52.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去哪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.65,0:15:53.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点事情…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.42,0:15:56.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.55,0:15:58.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 打扰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.69,0:16:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我叫做速水\N-我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.16,0:16:13.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天救我们的是芝村同学没错吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.30,0:16:17.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实壬生屋应该也要来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.44,0:16:20.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是尽军人的义务罢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.81,0:16:23.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是那毕竟是我的失误
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.78,0:16:24.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.95,0:16:29.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为害你也遭受危险 所以想来跟你道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.18,0:16:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.59,0:16:33.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对、对不起…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.69,0:16:36.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.09,0:16:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要道歉之前先把工作做好 会失误的话就多努力点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.56,0:16:42.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要没事就嘻皮笑脸的 或是随便向别人低头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.33,0:16:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.47,0:16:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你为什么要道歉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.73,0:16:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.60,0:16:52.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是因为这样 所以才会被说是呆呆的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.84,0:16:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呆呆？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.58,0:16:56.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问呆呆是指…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.98,0:16:58.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.61,0:17:00.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 是男人就果断一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.32,0:17:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 那我告辞了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.22,0:17:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是很感谢你的帮忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.50,0:17:19.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fnsimhei}(现在报导八代地区的被害状况)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.23,0:17:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fnsimhei}(目前仍在搜寻失踪民众 不过作业似乎遇到瓶颈)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.27,0:17:28.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.51,0:17:32.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,望望美 今天真早呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.75,0:17:35.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我肚子饿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.75,0:17:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗是吗 多吃点 赶快长大喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.76,0:17:44.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要跌倒喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.04,0:17:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.80,0:17:58.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以坐这里吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.28,0:18:04.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问小舞是大功臣吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.95,0:18:05.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大功臣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.11,0:18:09.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你救了小志跟未央啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.55,0:18:12.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就是大功臣咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.62,0:18:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不记得说过你救过我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.96,0:18:21.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不记得有救过你呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.83,0:18:28.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以吵架啦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.07,0:18:35.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在生气吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.35,0:18:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师说未央不太懂礼貌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.49,0:18:47.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过未央是望望美的好朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.32,0:18:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以小舞也要跟她好喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.33,0:18:55.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真纪你看 好多泡泡喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.86,0:18:59.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要这样 会沾到眼睛的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.60,0:19:00.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.12,0:19:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不太懂礼貌吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.16,0:19:23.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.89,0:19:28.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我以前用的尺寸 不太合就别太在意啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.36,0:19:30.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.36,0:19:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 那就明天见啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.03,0:19:34.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加藤同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.14,0:19:39.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我祭就可以了 你那样叫我会不好意思的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.18,0:19:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.05,0:19:55.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不太善于跟别人说话 不知道大家会不会觉得我很奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.39,0:19:58.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家应该都不会介意吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.43,0:20:01.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我虽然很喜欢说话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.66,0:20:04.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过要我注意说话细节 我一定会受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.67,0:20:08.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何况我们班本来就都是些奇怪的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.90,0:20:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不这么认为吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.21,0:20:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小布 吃饭罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.48,0:20:49.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚去哪里了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.61,0:20:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.72,0:21:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受不了 他真是个怪家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.02,0:21:47.66,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}最重要的心情 总是过于接近无法传达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.00,0:22:00.04,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}擦肩而过时的悲伤 在我的内心紧紧纠结
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.28,0:22:05.62,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}雨过天睛 光珠般的雨滴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.35,0:22:11.62,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}我将其收集起来 藉以思念你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.19,0:22:19.36,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}没人知道我将前往何处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.53,0:22:25.80,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}只有明日的风描绘着我的轨迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.07,0:22:31.57,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}随着时代变动的我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.85,0:22:37.58,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}即使迷失在困惑里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.58,0:22:43.89,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}也要抱紧这相遇的奇迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.16,0:22:54.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 一同前去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.17,0:22:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.07,0:22:58.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中元节也来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.67,0:23:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中元节让大家回忆起往事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.91,0:23:04.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回忆往事有点令人寂寞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.11,0:23:09.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寂寞似乎跟难过划上了等号…
